long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
With Go Jacktra, you can raise money for charity by simply opening new browsers, reading articles and searching the web. Just by surfing the web, you can feed shelter animals, and help animals in need.

Go Jacktra transforms your "new tab" page. Each time you open a tab, you will be greeted with our homepage, an incredible new tab page filled that is customizable for you. Here you can read articles on topics you like which will be coming soon, search the web, use our custom widgets and browse the web. With ads such as custom widgets, native ads, banner ads, and search ads, we're able to collect ad revenue and use it to donate to animals all around the world in need!

By clicking "Add to chrome", I accept and agree to installing the Go Jacktra Search extension, allowing the Jacktra extension to be your New Tab page and setting Chromeâ„¢ to that provided by the service and the Terms of Use and Privacy Policy.

Learn more at: https://gojacktra.com/about-us


Your Privacy Matters
Go Jacktra is committed to protecting your privacy and using your data responsibly. We save information relevant to your profile on Go Jacktra (such as your engine preferences and new tab page widgets). We do not collect any information we do not need.

The new tab page & our homepage contain advertisements that help us raise money for charity. These ads are delivered by our advertising partners. These partners may collect anonymized data about you in order to show you ads you'll be interested in.

For more info, check out our privacy policy:
https://gojacktra.com/privacy-policy
